snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda Nes Remake - Trailer
snippet.description:
Download ► https://lloydempty.itch.io/the-legend-of-zelda-era-of-decline

The playable beta is now available!
Do not hesitate to send me your comments

After a little more than a year of development on UE4 I am pleased to present you this first trailer, The Legend of Zelda Era Of Decline project.

Composer: Alcibiade Minel
https://soundcloud.com/alcibiade-minel
